data.description: Come see this charming split-level gem that combines older craftsmanship with contemporary comforts. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence spans over 2,100 square feet. The updated kitchen boasts new granite countertops, backsplash, cabinets, and tile flooring. All bathrooms were updated with tile flooring and granite counters. There are also new ceiling fans throughout.  Downstairs, you'll find a finished basement. Whether you're a sports enthusiast, movie buff, or just enjoy a cozy spot to unwind, this basement has it all. Complete with a bar/lounge area with a TV, it creates the perfect space for game day or movie night. Next step outside to the covered patio which provides a comfortable atmosphere for all your outdoor gatherings. If you enjoy working with our hands, you'll love the detached two-car garage with a wired workshop underneath. It's perfect for hobbies, projects, or extra storage needs. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
